nodes.text: Wilst Molan was a Human female dancer who worked at the Outlander Club on Coruscant. In 22 BBY, she was present when Zam Wesell was apprehended by Obi-Wan Kenobi. Wilst Molan had a special hair style which slightly resembled the horns of the Gotal, wore a special jewel on her forehead, and adorned greenish makeup around her eyes, which was Thoadeye-style makeup.
